parameters:
A skilled magician conducting magic research for
warriors... Oh my, I wonder if there are any willing
participants for collaboration.

Skilled magician, would you be willing to help me with my
research as a reliable warrior?
Will you engage in a duel?
Hmm... Another test subject has escaped, huh?

Skilled magician, this is much appreciated! It's time for a
fun experiment!

Skilled magician, there is still room for improvement. I
would appreciate it if you could cooperate with me anytime.

Skilled magician, hmm... You're not very helpful. Please
come back after you've improved your skills a bit more.

It's for your own good not to get involved with the
teacher, Magical Assistant.

Mage's Assistant: It's for your own good not to get
involved with the teacher.
